ListMap<Long,V>, Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<V>, Collection<V>, List<V>, RandomAccess
public class LongArrayListMap<V extends Identifiable<Long>>
extends ArrayList<V>
implements ListMap<Long,V>

This is a ListMap implementation that maps Long to a Object. This implementation uses a LongSparseArray and an ArrayList as internal data structure.

Author:
Hannes Dorfmann
